**Code changes (`index.html`):**

- **`TripCard`** — now accepts `me` and `onSettings` props. Derives `isCreator` from `trip.ownerId === me.id`. For creators: renders a gear icon (top-right of cover, same pill style as the date badge) that calls `onSettings()` on click with `stopPropagation`. For joined members: renders an orange "Joined" badge in the same position, and a muted "by [Name]" line below the trip title.
