- **"Completed"** badge overlaid on the hero image
- A read-only notice banner below the hero (with completion date and restore hint for admins)
- All edit controls hidden across all tabs: no add/delete buttons in Overview, Crew, Meals, Costs, or Itinerary; field notes and emergency contacts render as static text

